Name: The Guild Garage
Title: All the Crown Vic Feels
Desc: It's finally time to fire up the Model T, before some extensive bodywork that will keep Kalev busy.
LongDescription: It's finally time to fire up the Model T, before some extensive bodywork that will keep Kalev busy for a while. The Crown Vic gets a visit from her owners, before Greg goes on her final road test. Dave and Janice visit the Lane Motor Museum in Nashv.
